<li><strong>Hip Measurement</strong>: Wrap the measuring tape around the fu=
llest part of your hips, making sure to keep the tape parallel to the floor=
. </li>



<li><strong>Shoulder Measurement</strong>: Measure from the tip of one shou=
lder, across your back, to the tip of the other shoulder. </li>



