rong>Torso Measurement</strong></a>: Measure from the top of your shoulder,=
 down the front of your body, to the desired length of the dress.</li>



<li><strong>Sleeve Length</strong>: Measure from the top of your shoulder, =
down your arm, to the desired length of the sleeve.</li>



<li><strong>Compare your measurements</strong> to the size chart of the dre=
ss you want to purchase to ensure the best fit.</li>
</ol>



